The suite of tests included in this section run against a basic form with
all the controls needed to test Fitnium. The form can be viewed online at

If you have configured Fitnium to run with Jetty as a local http server, then the files
are hosted at :

http://localhost:8090/fitnium/testpage4api.html

Its not designed to be a perfect form, just the right content for the tests

